  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "chapterTitle": "厄舍府之倒塌",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "934600_4_942-1050",
          "range": "942-1050",
          "rangeStart": 942,
          "rangeEnd": 1050,
          "markText": "我心中极度的抑郁真难用人间常情来比拟，也许只能比作鸦片服用者清醒后的感受：重新堕入现实生活之痛苦、重新撩开那层面纱之恐惧。我感到一阵冰凉、一阵虚脱、一阵心悸、一阵无法摆脱的凄怆、一阵任何想象力都无法将其理想化的悲凉。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1719361520,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-26 08:25:20",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=934600&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=942&rangeEnd=1050",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6bb329005e42c86bbfa8648?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=942&rangeEnd=1050"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "934600_4_2148-2185",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2148-2185",
      "markText": "我早就知晓，那种迷信是一种似是而非的法则：即人类所有感情都以恐惧为其基础。",
      "totalCount": 976,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=934600&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2148&rangeEnd=2185",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6bb329005e42c86bbfa8648?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2148&rangeEnd=2185"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "934600_16_16462-16545",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "16462-16545",
      "markText": "你已经获胜，而我输了。但从今以后你也就死去，对这个世界、对天堂和希望也就毫无感觉！你存在于我中，而我一死，请看这个影子吧，这是你自己的影子，看你多么彻底地扼杀了自己。",
      "totalCount": 720,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=934600&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=16462&rangeEnd=16545",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6bb329005e42c86bbfa8648?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=16462&rangeEnd=16545"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "934600_4_711-780",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "711-780",
      "markText": "那年秋天一个晦暝、昏暗、廓落、云幕低垂的日子，我一整天都策马独行，穿越一片异常阴郁的旷野。当暮色开始降临时，愁云笼罩的厄舍府终于遥遥在望。",
      "totalCount": 680,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=934600&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=711&rangeEnd=780",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6bb329005e42c86bbfa8648?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=711&rangeEnd=780"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "934600_8_14078-14146",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "14078-14146",
      "markText": "“那么，至少，”我失声惊呼，“至少我不会弄错，我绝不会弄错，这双圆圆的、乌黑的、目光热切的眼睛，属于我失去的爱人！属于她！属于丽姬娅！”",
      "totalCount": 600,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=934600&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=14078&rangeEnd=14146",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6bb329005e42c86bbfa8648?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=14078&rangeEnd=14146"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "934600_5_1021-1110",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1021-1110",
      "markText": "亲王早就做好了寻欢作乐的一切安排。宅内有插科打诨的小丑，有即席吟诵的诗人，有表演芭蕾的舞女，有演奏音乐的乐师，而且还有美女和酒浆。所有的欢乐和平安都在墙内。墙外则是红死病的天下。",
      "totalCount": 480,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=934600&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1021&rangeEnd=1110",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6bb329005e42c86bbfa8648?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1021&rangeEnd=1110"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "934600_4_2358-2385",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2358-2385",
      "markText": "那是一种神秘而致命的雾霭，阴晦，凝滞，朦胧，沉浊如铅。",
